<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.5.1">
<l>pūṅkōtai yāycci kaṭaiveṇṇey pukkuṇṇa</l>
<l>vāṅkava ḷārttup puṭaikkap puṭaiyuṇṭu</l>
<l>vēṅki yiruntu ciṇuṅki viḷaiyāṭum</l>
<l>ōṅkōta vaṇṇaṉē cappāṇi</l>
<l rend="indent">yoḷimaṇi  vaṇṇaṉē cappāṇi.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You, the hue of swelling waves, who played at whining,</l>
<l>Sitting wailing, since entering [the house], you ate butter</l>
<l>Which the herdess, with flower[-filled] hair, churned,</l>
<l>Being beaten, when she beat [you], tying you there, clap your hands;</l>
<l rend="indent">my shining jewel, clap your hands!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
